{"tid":1787072,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫委會醫生委員直選　何栢良蔡堅高票連任　盧寵茂落選","createTime":"2019-12-17T15:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T06:12:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c3e280b7fdbf7c263975f830653b3c80873e00","tid":1787072,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20191217-17_kDOPb_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20191217-17_kDOPb_1200x0.png&h=2f636a15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醫務委員會早前就兩個醫生委員席位進行直選，今日公布結果。競逐連任的港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良及醫學會前會長蔡堅，以超過 5,000 票成功當選，組團隊參選的港大深圳醫院院長盧寵茂及私人執業皮膚及性病科專科醫生陳衍里，則只獲不足 2,000 票，雙雙落選。<br />\n<br />\n今次兩個直選席位由香港全體醫生一人一票選出，今日公布結果。根據香港公共醫療醫生協會 facebook 專頁上載的資料，勝出的蔡堅獲得 5199 票，何栢良得到 5147 票，盧寵茂僅得 1597 票落選，另一候選人陳衍里得 1088 票。<br />\n<br />\n是次選舉被視為「黃藍之爭」，反送中運動期間，前醫學會會長蔡堅接受傳媒訪問時稱他多次上街，並曾於伊利沙伯醫院醫護集會中上台，公開大罵政府：「而家呢個狗屎垃圾政府，聽到市民嘅聲音，但堅持唔做嘢。」港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良亦曾於瑪麗醫院醫護集會批評有部分警務人員使用不恰當武力，又斥林鄭月娥沒履行「化解社會撕裂、聆聽市民」的競選承諾。<br />\n<br />\n醫務委員會根據香港法例第161章《醫生註冊條例》成立，由 24 名醫生和 8 名業外委員組成，獲賦予權力處理本港執業醫生的註冊和紀律規管事宜<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%86%AB%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E7%9B%B4%E9%81%B8-%E4%BD%95%E6%A0%A2%E8%89%AF%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85%E9%AB%98%E7%A5%A8%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB-%E7%9B%A7%E5%AF%B5%E8%8C%82%E8%90%BD%E9%81%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%259B%25B4%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%25A0%25A2%25E8%2589%25AF%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E9%2580%25A3%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E8%258C%2582%25E8%2590%25BD%25E9%2581%25B8%2F&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2BusF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=9df8d808\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%259B%25B4%25E9%2581%25B8-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%25A0%25A2%25E8%2589%25AF%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E9%2580%25A3%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E8%258C%2582%25E8%2590%25BD%25E9%2581%25B8%2F&h=a9380b19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%86%AB%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E7%9B%B4%E9%81%B8-%E4%BD%95%E6%A0%A2%E8%89%AF%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85%E9%AB%98%E7%A5%A8%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB-%E7%9B%A7%E5%AF%B5%E8%8C%82%E8%90%BD%E9%81%B8/</a>"},{"pid":"1b2c4a1ec70e66440d4905048801cf05344a031f","tid":1787072,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb2165daf800b81bdddd5690138ee9d5963dcf0","tid":1787072,"uid":108337,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"藍絲只係少數派, 係阻住社會進步既垃圾"},{"pid":"24dae6d75082ada7b33a0a0baf764cba8982c4df","tid":1787072,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb2165daf800b81bdddd5690138ee9d5963dcf0","tid":1787072,"uid":108337,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:37:00.000Z","msg":"藍絲只係少數派, 係阻住社會進步既垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /